{"tid":580462,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵班志同道合既朋友仔","createTime":"2018-03-04T14:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T05:50:21.000Z","uid":174235,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bf5a831f83d666cebc6a5c2800e5faf087df7d54","tid":580462,"uid":174235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T14:04:37.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人好似我咁，鐘意影相拍片想做同media有關既行業（終極目標係想拍電影做導演），但係大學本科讀既野完全唔撚關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 身邊又冇朋友有係呢方面既共同興趣，自己一個由0開始孤軍作戰咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想係連登招個兵買個馬，搵班同自己一樣鐘意度橋拍野但又苦於冇伴既fd子，組隊crew出黎共同發奮。<br />\n講下我自己先，讀緊某大學中文系，有文學底，所以係寫劇本呀諗故仔方面都幾有自信。<br />\n近排開始練緊攝影同埋學Photoshop同 premiere，但只係新手水平，所以真係好希望可以係度搵到一齊學習同一步一步product屬於自己既作品既戰友們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只要係年齡相近性格平易近人好相處既朋友仔（18~25）都可以，有興趣既巴絲就add telegram la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/satoriu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsatoriu&d=lgxXzZurIh5JK5ta4sEVTzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=77ae8083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/satoriu</a><br />\n<br />\n希望add既朋友係真心真意想一齊做野學野唔係假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea35459840f965bf068a189f8d54bd8d2498077c","tid":580462,"uid":174235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T01:15:08.000Z","msg":"推~"},{"pid":"68d39d3f799bc2040f286ed765c45cada2015bb5","tid":580462,"uid":6587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T04:26:05.000Z","msg":"睇完成段嘢再望一望你個名........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\